WEBVTT

00:01.311 --> 00:03.244
[mysterious exotic music]

00:03.279 --> 00:06.247
[man singing
in foreign language]

00:06.282 --> 00:11.045
♪

00:11.080 --> 00:12.840
- The warrior Bhima

00:12.874 --> 00:15.670
is tricked into
a fool's errand.

00:15.705 --> 00:18.190
- [singing in foreign language]

00:18.225 --> 00:21.055
- He seeks his parents
in heaven.

00:21.090 --> 00:22.505
They are not there.

00:22.539 --> 00:25.715
Instead, he finds them
in hell.

00:25.749 --> 00:26.923
♪

00:26.957 --> 00:29.098
He offers his parents
the elixir of life,

00:29.132 --> 00:31.100
yet they refuse.

00:31.134 --> 00:34.103
They accept the fruits
of their karma.

00:34.137 --> 00:35.345
♪

00:35.380 --> 00:37.347
This being their final test,

00:37.382 --> 00:40.247
they ascend to heaven.

00:40.281 --> 00:41.593
- [vocalizing]

00:41.627 --> 00:44.389
- The story of Bhima Swarga
teaches us that heaven

00:44.423 --> 00:46.253
and hell are allegories.

00:46.287 --> 00:48.082
Not truths.

00:48.117 --> 00:50.119
Life is cyclical,

00:50.153 --> 00:51.741
and so is death.

00:51.775 --> 00:54.123
- [vocalizing]

00:54.157 --> 00:56.090
♪

00:56.125 --> 00:57.712
[upbeat rock music]

